<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#1a2a6c">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
  <title>Page non trouvée - GeoAlert</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  
  <style>
    /* ============================================
       PAGE D'ERREUR 404 - RESPONSIVE
       ============================================ */
    
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c 0%, #2a3f8f 50%, #b21f1f 100%);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .error-container {
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      animation: bounce-in 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
    }
    
    @keyframes bounce-in {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.85);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }
    
    /* EMOJI ERREUR */
    .error-emoji {
      font-size: 64px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0;
      animation: shake 0.6s ease-in-out;
    }
    
    @keyframes shake {
      0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      25% { transform: rotate(-5deg); }
      75% { transform: rotate(5deg); }
    }
    
    /* CODE D'ERREUR */
    .error-code {
      font-size: 72px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #b21f1f;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }
    
    /* TITRE ERREUR */
    .error-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a2a6c;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    
    /* MESSAGE ERREUR */
    .error-message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #666;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* BOUTON RETOUR */
    .home-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(26, 42, 108, 0.35);
      border: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    
    .home-link:hover,
    .home-link:focus {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(26, 42, 108, 0.45);
    }
    
    .home-link:active {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(26, 42, 108, 0.3);
    }
    
    /* RESPONSIVE MOBILE < 480px */
    @media (max-width: 479px) {
      body {
        padding: 16px;
      }
      
      .error-container {
        padding: 32px 16px;
        gap: 16px;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
      
      .error-emoji {
        font-size: 52px;
      }
      
      .error-code {
        font-size: 56px;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .error-message {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      
      .home-link {
        min-height: 44px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 14px;
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
    
    /* RESPONSIVE TABLET 480px - 768px */
    @media (min-width: 480px) and (max-width: 767px) {
      .error-container {
        padding: 40px 24px;
      }
      
      .error-emoji {
        font-size: 60px;
      }
      
      .error-code {
        font-size: 64px;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 26px;
      }
    }
    
    /* RESPONSIVE DESKTOP >= 768px */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
      
      .error-container {
        padding: 60px 40px;
        gap: 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      }
      
      .error-emoji {
        font-size: 80px;
      }
      
      .error-code {
        font-size: 88px;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 36px;
      }
      
      .error-message {
        font-size: 16px;
        max-width: 400px;
      }
      
      .home-link {
        min-height: 52px;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <span class="error-emoji">🗺️❌</span>
    <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
    <h2 class="error-title">Page non trouvée</h2>
    <p class="error-message">Désolé, la page que vous recherchez n'existe pas ou a été supprimée.</p>
    <a href="/" class="home-link">🏠 Retour à l'accueil</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>